item.title: About
item.description: 🌺 Note from the Editor This is me! If you’re looking to contact me, write to me Here. 🤹🏻‍♂️ About # Hobart Phillips is an Australian illustrator and writer living and working in Tasmania. He’s 22 going on 23, and wears the same white shirt and black trousers every day. He likes machines, midcentury architecture and Tasmania.
